{"tid":2235942,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是日晚餐，椒麻雞x蔥油雞","createTime":"2020-10-09T05:48:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T10:19:50.000Z","uid":93141,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"fd739e7653357f4216c7ce89bfeaf81b69cebf26","tid":2235942,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T05:48:24.000Z","msg":"是日好hea既餐，但好適合響屋企做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MwYSXYB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMwYSXYB.jpg&h=3b7e6617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n椒麻雞 材料:雞腿肉，蒜頭，辣椒，芫荽，花生，豉油，魚露，青檸，胡椒，鹽<br />\n<br />\n雞肉用胡椒同鹽醃過後，抹走雞皮表面水份，細火皮向下落煎pan煎到金黃，保留雞油<br />\n蒜頭，辣椒，芫荽，花生切碎，加豉油，魚露同青檸汁，調味後食前淋上雞肉就得<br />\n<br />\n蔥油雞 材料: 雞腿肉，蔥，薑，月桂葉，鹽，雞油<br />\n用鹽，蔥段同薑片開滾水，滾後加入雞肉同月桂葉，熄火等25分鐘，過後攞出雞肉擺入冰水<br />\n蔥切碎，薑磨蓉，加入煎雞時用既雞油同煮雞既雞湯，少少鹽調味後，食前淋上雞肉就得<br />\n<br />\n雞飯  材料: 米，雞油，蒜瓣，薑片，丁香，月桂葉，雞湯<br />\n用雞油爆香蒜瓣同薑片，加入洗過既米炒到有油光<br />\n加兩倍份量雞湯，丁香同月桂葉，煮熟就搞掂<br />\n<br />\nGin and tonic請睇上一篇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0bda2ad22073c15fcafb1600f3fc2f9aa03e58f","tid":2235942,"uid":93141,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T05:48:46.000Z","msg":"Rare image of my roommate唔識用筷子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kpQ6hZc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkpQ6hZc.png&h=4d1bcb8e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9fb8f304e477f40b346a6096e515bff168f62049","tid":2235942,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T05:49:10.000Z","msg":"靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faeaf00fde7566d8c10ee82524dfe5f0ad9b51c8","tid":2235942,"uid":93141,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T05:49:48.000Z","msg":"Rare image of 樓豬做緊tutor<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HwS06ST.jpg\" data-thumbnai